    • Constructor Detail

      • DataItem

        public DataItem(java.lang.String itemId)
        create a new data item structure.

        Note that the item is initially unconnected

        Parameters:
        itemId - the id of the item to register later

      • DataItem

        public DataItem(java.lang.String itemId,
        ItemManager itemManager)
        create a new data item structure.

        Note that the item is initially connected to the item manager provided. You must call unregister() when you want to clear the subscription with the item on the server.

        Parameters:
        itemId - the id of the item to register
        itemManager - the item manager to which the item will register
